---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

I got this idea from watching my brother play "Nazi Zombie" on COD5. Basically, there are 4 humans and the rest are zombies. The humans need to hold the zombies off for 150 seconds. Once 90 seconds pass, the humans will be allowed to unlock a bomb shelter door from a button that is inside one of the bedrooms. The humans must then fight their way into the bomb shelter (outside) to survive and win the round. 

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

****CTS****
 - Get to pick a gun from two tables at spawn.
 - Get teled into the 2nd floor of house after 20 seconds.
 - Have 100 HP.

****TS****
 - Get to choose one of three classes
 - Spawn on one of the sides of the house (outside).

**CLASSES**

Skinny zombie
 - 500 HP
 - 1.25 speed
 - Light Green

Normal zombie
 - 1000 HP
 - 1.00 speed
 - Green

Fat zombie
 - 2000 HP
 - 0.75 speed
 - Dark Green

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

****NOTES****
- TS can't pick up guns.
- CTS can only leave a house if a zombie gets in or if the bomb shelter has been unlocked.
-  After 30 seconds, the humans will be allowed to blow up the front door. Blowing up the front door will kill any zombies near it but will make it a lot easier for the zombies to get in and attack you.
- Humans and zombies can break the wood covering the windows. So be careful and dont shoot the wood!

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

****PICTURES****
1. The outside of the house.
2. The inside of the bomb shelter.
3. CT spawn
4. T spawn
5. The button to unlock the bomb shelter door.
6. The C4 that will blow up the front.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

I don't know how good the gameplay is going to be, so please leave a comment below if one of the teams overpowers another too easily. If there are any glitches or if the gameplay is too bad, I will make a v2 for this map. :)

The first T or CT that reaches the triforce at the top, will be link. Everyone else will be monsters. The player that becomes link will get teled to the center of a lava and will get a sword. Everyone else will get teled to a different area that has a bunch of red and blue block monsters (red for Ts and blue for CTs). The Ts and CTs will have 10 seconds to pick a monster. If a player in a monster suit touches the player that is link, it will hurt link 10 dmg every half a second. There is a white monster suit on each team, that does 20 dmg every half a second. The player that is link can either knife the monsters, or push them into the lava with the sword.

The song is a rock verson of the Gerudo Valley Theme song.

FIXES

 -Fixed problem where alot of Ts and CTs died when they touched the "monster" suit.
 -Lowered the damage the "monsters" do to "link"
 -Lowered the speed of the push from "link's" sword

In this map your object is to reach the ZeiZei's office, which is located at the top floor of this building.
On your way up you will come across with several deadly traps, and it is recommended that you try to get past them alive.

I also made this map alternating, so there are multiple different ways with different traps. And of course, map chooses the way up randomly.

I'm not asking you to rate or comment, but I would love to read some feedback

I just hope you like it!

Hello everybody, it's been a long time...

It's been 4 years since my last map upload here on gamebanana, and I have to say time really flies by. Today I decided to upload sequel to the original mg_zeizeiii . 

I made this map back in 2013 i think, but never released it here. Thats why you may have seen it somewhere before. This map as previous one is rather "easy" course map with a lot to discover. Over 25 levels to play through and a lot of secrets etc. 

It is really stupid to say this because it's been so long time from previous map upload, but this map features different soundtrack to each "worlds", which I learned myself just for this map. But I have to say, there are some missing textures on some levels which makes me and probably you a bit mad, but I can't do anything for that because I made this 3years ago and lost a lot of the material etc. Hope you understand. To mention it is just a couple levels, nothing serious(I hope).

To notify you, this is not the "original" map. The "original" one is mg_ZeiZeiii_2 which I made first. But because players thought it was a bit too hard I made this easier version. If you would like to play the original harder one, please write a comment and I can upload it here too.

And what comes to the texture creators, I cannot remember the names anymore, but if you spot your texture on this map you can comment about it and I will add you to credits. All the downloaded textures was downloaded from here, gamebanana, so I'll check the profiles uploads to confirm.

Thank you all "veterans" who liked my maps 4-5 years back, and I hope all the good for you, and for you newer hosts and players, keep the flag of css high!!

Whooof, after that, I have to say that I am officially being retired from css map making (having being for 3years for now) because life goes on and one grows up, I would love to make content, but becaming adult means less freetime, and on top of that i think css community isn't the same again. It might be because im a lot older now, but thats just how i feel.

I hope you enjoy this map, it have been a wild ride during those 3000hours of css.

Love you, bye


PS. I also made mg_ZeiZeiii_Xmas map which is xmas edition of the mg_ZeiZeiii(with completely different levels ofc(and before this map)), so if you doesn't have that yet and would like to, mention it in the comments ;D

HELLO!

I made this map couple months ago, tested it in my friends minigame server and I was suprised how much it got good feedback. So I decided to upload it here. 

Anyways, this map is rather short including 25 good looking and well made levels. There are also many awesome textures, some made by me and other downloaded from here,  credits can bee seen at the end of the map. I also made music that plays background. When you have finished the map there are still a lot to do, 2 bonus levels and secrets all around the map. So you wont be bored!:D

I made this map to be "easy", so everyone should pass through this obstacle course.
I hope you like it, give me feedback and don't forget to rate!:DD

INCLUDES SUPER HIGH FPS!!!

knife arena - you get 35 hp and you are on map with large pit, you can hear 'this is sparta remix' song

paintball - you get mp5 and 1 hp and then it's up to you and your team

rotating rope - you spawn in a room and after few seconds rope starts to rotate, each wave you survive, you get 10 score points, you can hear 'meatspin' music at the background

course - you spawn on a grass and your goal is to finish the course first without dying. The one who gets to the finish is awarded by 10 score points

climb - you spawn in a deep hole and your goal is to climb up, you can hear annoying music at the background, the one who gets to the top will be awarded by 10 score points

zombie survival - random team will be set as zombies / humans. As humans you have 10 seconds to find a weapon and find yourself a safe place to survive. As zombie you have to hunt down humans, you cannot pick up any gun but you have 3000 hp.

race - you spawn on a dusty ground and your goal is to get to the finish as first without rage quitting, be careful though because the time is limited.

hunt - random team will be set as hunters / victims. As victims you need to hide in a big house, you have one flashbang and that's it, you need to wait for police arrival. As hunters you have knife but you need to wait 20 seconds until you are released into the house, then you just need to kill all of them until the time runs out.
The map is about you spawn at a platform, you go down and complete the dodge arena, after the dodge arena you come to a shotgun arena where it is T vs CT.

MG YOLO MULTIGAMES

MAP INFO

A multigame level with 14 maps to choose from. - Football (2 easter eggs) (1HP or 100HP) - Fruits - Elevator - AWP - Headshot (not headshot only) - Grenade Holes - Hot Potato (Can only be played once) - Knife - Creeper - Blocks - Pistols - 1HP Smoke Skate - Volleyball - Aim Tower (2 easter eggs) (By C y a n) I know the map name is gay but I couldn't think of anything more suiting. If you add this map to your server please post the IP below so I can come and join.

Change Log

v1 First version of map released.

At the start of the map you start in a black screen with white words, I HIGHLY recommend everyone read this to figure out what is going on.

You will spawn randomly as one of eight characters. Each character has a different colour button indicator light.
Beast:Navy
Cyclops:Red
Wolverine:Yellow
Iceman:Cyan
Rogue:Orange
Storm:White
Nightcrawler:Purple
Quicksilver:Green

The light shows whether your button is enabled or disabled, if the light is off, you can't activate your ability. If it is on, you can.

Spawning in the building means you are a mutant. You must protect Magneto's helmet from being destroyed by the clones.

Spawning outside means you are a clone, infiltrate the building and destroy Magneto's helmet. (First you must destroy the generator to power-down the door guarding his helmet.)

There are hints (just above the map time) that help give you an idea of who you are.
It tells you whether you are a mutant, or a clone, and which character you are. It also tells you what your ability does.

Beast:Low gravity, slightly increased speed, and a small health regeneration.
Cyclops:Highly damaging laser. Must be aimed well!
Wolverine:Heals self 50 hp. Can not go above 100 hp.
Iceman:Freezes all enemies within radius for a few seconds.
Rogue:Disables enemies abilities, also shuts down currently active abilities.
Storm:Lightning rains down damaging all enemies within radius.
Nightcrawler:Teleports a set distance. Use button light as distance indicator. (Teleporting out of map=teleported to the main, outside area.)
Quicksilver:Increased speed for short duration.

Work together!
Having a Rogue nearby is extremely helpful, yet Rogue on her own is not nearly as good.

Thanks TAG (tagservers.com) for letting me use their private server to do my testing on! :D
Have fun!

mg_xmas_nipperhouse

 Nipper made an awesome work at making this map.

[SG] Paul modified it after, and added many things to make the map Hide and Seek and more fun. Like overlays, console messages, commands. He modified it on his server with a plugin, by adding new things like a mini size for ct (more hides), and a santa skin for terrorist, or give a m249 after a timelimit to the winner. But all these changes used non-official Sourcemod plugins.

I made the same change he did for his server, and I added a few more things. It's not anymore plugin-dependant.
What To Do.

CT = Hide for 3 minutes in the house, and outside. You have a reduced size, so you can go in many spots. Your speed is a little faster than the T.

T = After 30 seconds, you can move and start to hunt the CT. You have a Santa skin, a Knife, and a normal size.

After 3 minutes, CT get a M249, and can kill the Terrorist who also get ignited 10 seconds after to slowly kill them ^^

Feature
  • Santa Skin made by S-Low
  • Many Overlays with Sounds that are triggered randomly in the map (made by [SG] Paul)
  • "Jingle Bell" music
  • Mini-Sized CT
  • Santa T
  • An "hidden" mini santa. It does something if you press E on it.

What Else ?

 I modified the whole map with EntSpy, so I didnt decompiled anything. If I decompiled the map, it would have been broken.
Some spots were unreachable by the T, so the CT where invulnerable there. I added some push to block these spots.

T - Your are a monster you have 3 chances to kill every CT before you yourself is killed. Each stage you will get a different monster which has a different ability.

Stage 1 - Antlion, gets a charge ability.

Stage 2 - Cyclope, gets a stomp ability.

Stage 3 - Pedobear, once near a enemy grips onto them and kills them.

CT - You start with a m4a1 and a deagle, if you run out of ammo check the stock infront of your spawn. 

Tatics - 

Antlion - Keep away from his front as you will take damage best to take him fron behind. ( Sounds Very Wrong )

Cyclope - Keep a fair distance away from his feet apart from that you can pretty much stand anywhere.

Pedobear - Spread out keep away from each other. Keep as far away from him as you can.
